These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, guinea-pig, pony
House: victorian, cottage, futuristic, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, fanta, cola
There 4 different types of food: pepper, grapefruit, strawberry, garlic
 1. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 2. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person eating pepper##8
 3. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
 5. the person eating pepper is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
 6. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
 8. the art-deco house is between the person eating grapefruit and the person drinking sprite##2
 9. the person eating garlic is the futuristic house##1
10. the person eating garlic is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
12. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
13. the futuristic house is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
14. the owner of the snake is the person eating strawberry##1
15. the owner of the snake is not the person drinking sprite##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | rat     | snake   | pony | guinea-pig |
| House   | cottage | art-deco   | victorian   | futuristic  |
| Beverage         | sprite  | fanta  | cola  | 7up |
| Food     | pepper    | strawberry | grapefruit     | garlic    |

