 4. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the designer##8
 5. the lawyer is not to the left of the person who growsiris##8
 6. the davidoff-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 7. the mechanic is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
 8. the mechanic is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who growstulip is the freelancer##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
11. the lawyer is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
14. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
15. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
16. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
