 3. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 4. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
 5. the argentine is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 6. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 7. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the mexican is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the scientist##8
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the mexican##3

