There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, soul, hip-hop, classical
 1. the tower house is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the tower house is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 6. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 7. the wooden house is in an odd position##4
 8. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
 9. the wooden house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of soul is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
13. the tower house is on the right of the palace house##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
15. the palace house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
