 6. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
 7. the tower house is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
 8. the person driving the train is the person who growslily##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is not to the left of the person playing monopoly##8
10. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
11. the cottage house is between the person playing monopoly and the person who growslily##2
12. the person playing poker is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
13. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
