4 different games are played: snooker, bridge, poker, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, climbing, ice-hockey
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, filmmaking, traveling
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
