 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
 7. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6
 8. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the owner of the hamster##7
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
10. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
12. the person playing bridge is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
13. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
15. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
