 9. the photographer is somewhere between the person playing chess and the dancer##7
10. the photographer is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
11. the photographer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
12. the person who likes brown is not to the right of the chef##8
13. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing chess##1
14. the chef is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
