 6. the prince-smoker is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to london##7
 7. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##8
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the german and the russian##7
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
10. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
11. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
13. the prince-smoker is the german##1
14. the german is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
15. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
