.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, daisy, azalea
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pepper, zucchini, pear
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, snooker, whist
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut, orange, lavender
 1. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing whist##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 3. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 6. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 8. the person who likes chestnut is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
 9. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8
11. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4
13. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

